          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "After invoking this method, applying the receiver’s matrix modifies the unit length on the x axis by a factor of ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "scaleX",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " and the y axis by a factor of ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "scaleY",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ", in addition to performing all previous transformations. A value of 1.0 for either axis scales the content on that axis to the same size.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
